Announcing the appointment yesterday, Mr Frank Conroy, Westpac managing
director, portrayed it as part of a new growth phase for the bank.
'We have the problem loan provisioning behind us, and with completion of the
ADollars 1.2bn (USDollars 871.96m) rights issue on September 30, the bank's
