<HEADLINE>
FT  24 SEP 92 / World News in Brief: Bid to unfreeze Iraqi cash
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The US and its allies plan to press for a UN resolution to force the release
of hundreds of millions of dollars in frozen Iraqi funds from banks to pay
for UN inspections and humanitarian work in Iraq, a top Bush administration
official said.
